类 ResponseBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.cuter44.wxpay.resps.ResponseBase
  • 直接已知子类:
    Notify, UnifiedOrderResponse

    public class ResponseBase
extends java.lang.Object
    General response passed by req.execute() or alipay callback/redirect gateways Actually reqs/gateways passed excatly response type, i.e. sub-class of this. I'm recommending you to see the sub-class javadoc... to help you write elegant code.
